snippet.title: Game Boy Color - Kidou Senkan Nadesico - Ruriruri Mahjong © 1999 King Records - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Kidou Senkan Nadesico: Ruriruri Mahjong is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Studio Saizensen and published by King Records, which was released in Japan in 1999.
